title: Burrito Baby
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Tex-Mex
description: Mexican and Tex-Mex street food in a trendy, diner style eatery. Offers burritos, quesadilla, and tacos along with extras such as salad, rice, and beans. Offers children portions and a small selection of desserts. Sauces and beans are made-in-house. Most menu items could be made vegan, and the staff is knowledgeable about veganism.
